CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier, November 5, 1955, pg. 1B reads: "Dr. Azikiwe closes his official pouch. This bag is issued only to officials of the British Government.  Each bag has a number and a special key. - All photos, with exception of U. S. Steel, by Harris."
TitMainTitle: Eastern Nigerian Prime Minister Nnamdi Azikiwe wearing light colored agbada and dark cap, fastening attache case on table with Pittsburgh Courier Newspaper in interior
